{"tid":1785084,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"I 繼續講大丁啦］羅智光：保安局完成研究立法禁止侮辱公職人員　正徵詢律政司意見","createTime":"2019-12-16T06:27:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-16T09:58:14.000Z","uid":48083,"like":5,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"7686835817cfbc883870d454ccb75d80cf1decd1","tid":1785084,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T06:27:35.000Z","msg":"公務員事務局長羅智光今天在立法會一個委員會議上表示，保安局剛剛完成研究立法禁止侮辱公職人員的工作，正徵詢律政司的意見，下一步會再徵詢政策局意見，「我哋準備好會考慮點樣跟進，今日嚟講未有時間表。」<br />\n<br />\n至於有否機會在今年可提交予立法會討論，羅智光指不願作沒有基礎的估計。蔣麗芸指出，目前以難接受的言辭辱駡公務員的情況普遍，希望公務員事務局盡早立法，挽回公職人員的尊嚴。<br />\n<br />\n民建聯蔣麗芸和葛珮帆要早前要求公務員及資助機構員工事務委員會，討論立法禁止侮辱公職人員，認為近期挑釁和侮辱前線執勤公職人員的事件時有發生，言行越來越激烈，認為要求公職人員如聖人般，承受無上限的挑釁和侮辱是不實際，擔心會影響公職人員士氣，令香港充斥仇恨，要求將有關議題加入本年度的討論議程當中。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E7%BE%85%E6%99%BA%E5%85%89-%E4%BF%9D%E5%AE%89%E5%B1%80%E5%AE%8C%E6%88%90%E7%A0%94%E7%A9%B6%E7%AB%8B%E6%B3%95%E7%A6%81%E6%AD%A2%E4%BE%AE%E8%BE%B1%E5%85%AC%E8%81%B7%E4%BA%BA%E5%93%A1-%E6%AD%A3%E5%BE%B5%E8%A9%A2%E5%BE%8B%E6%94%BF%E5%8F%B8%E6%84%8F%E8%A6%8B/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E7%25BE%2585%25E6%2599%25BA%25E5%2585%2589-%25E4%25BF%259D%25E5%25AE%2589%25E5%25B1%2580%25E5%25AE%258C%25E6%2588%2590%25E7%25A0%2594%25E7%25A9%25B6%25E7%25AB%258B%25E6%25B3%2595%25E7%25A6%2581%25E6%25AD%25A2%25E4%25BE%25AE%25E8%25BE%25B1%25E5%2585%25AC%25E8%2581%25B7%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E5%2593%25A1-%25E6%25AD%25A3%25E5%25BE%25B5%25E8%25A9%25A2%25E5%25BE%258B%25E6%2594%25BF%25E5%258F%25B8%25E6%2584%258F%25E8%25A6%258B%2F&d=dVEf9brN%2BTtwApumOSMW7tB4iDtRAy51VXy1YCRVmoY%3D&h=9de9944f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E7%25BE%2585%25E6%2599%25BA%25E5%2585%2589-%25E4%25BF%259D%25E5%25AE%2589%25E5%25B1%2580%25E5%25AE%258C%25E6%2588%2590%25E7%25A0%2594%25E7%25A9%25B6%25E7%25AB%258B%25E6%25B3%2595%25E7%25A6%2581%25E6%25AD%25A2%25E4%25BE%25AE%25E8%25BE%25B1%25E5%2585%25AC%25E8%2581%25B7%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E5%2593%25A1-%25E6%25AD%25A3%25E5%25BE%25B5%25E8%25A9%25A2%25E5%25BE%258B%25E6%2594%25BF%25E5%258F%25B8%25E6%2584%258F%25E8%25A6%258B%2F&h=3b46e0c4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E7%BE%85%E6%99%BA%E5%85%89-%E4%BF%9D%E5%AE%89%E5%B1%80%E5%AE%8C%E6%88%90%E7%A0%94%E7%A9%B6%E7%AB%8B%E6%B3%95%E7%A6%81%E6%AD%A2%E4%BE%AE%E8%BE%B1%E5%85%AC%E8%81%B7%E4%BA%BA%E5%93%A1-%E6%AD%A3%E5%BE%B5%E8%A9%A2%E5%BE%8B%E6%94%BF%E5%8F%B8%E6%84%8F%E8%A6%8B/</a>"},{"pid":"8a359f767b38ca4d7516131d8292eeafbb527bd8","tid":1785084,"uid":34725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T06:27:59.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"eaa27709b9aee73763599f618ed9864357bc4928","tid":1785084,"uid":1882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T06:28:04.000Z","msg":"又黎多次十八<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49de71f7bd7a891f58e9e1869827e83523657704","tid":1785084,"uid":214997,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T06:29:06.000Z","msg":"They are well paid for it<br />\n唔想做咪唔好做咩無人逼佢"},{"pid":"d96de80a8e97febeeced808aaf0c29dd93fdf895","tid":1785084,"uid":335434,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T06:29:38.000Z","msg":"立法會議員同港台職員都係公職人員 咁班狗以後仲有無得週街用粗口屌鳩議員同港台記者呢?<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db1f7e272caa6c7891911f2dd3e5a3a44f442013","tid":1785084,"uid":267494,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T06:31:32.000Z","msg":"公職人員侮辱市民又唔立法？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f852c31ba9b95c7144c1218e1c846d98fccce8b","tid":1785084,"uid":63782,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T06:32:55.000Z","msg":"係咪唔記得立蒙面法嗰晚？"},{"pid":"f26ef5d9494785b247a0fa39429583979bbe2d38","tid":1785084,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T06:33:01.000Z","msg":"哩單好嚴重<img src=\"/assets/